OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,6,Fsome bright or sunny intervals. There
OL,7,Fwill be a few passing showers, but
OL,8,Fthese dying out through the afternoon.
OL,9,FFresh westerly winds backing
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly this afternoon, but
OL,11,Fstrong across Shetland this morning.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,14,Fsome clear periods. Then the rest of
OL,15,Fthe night will remain dry with clear
OL,16,Fperiods. Freshening southwesterly wind
OL,17,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
