OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FThe morning will be dry
OL,6,Fwith some brightness. Clouding over
OL,7,Ffrom the south in the afternoon with
OL,8,Fthe chance of a little rain by evening.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FCloudy on Thursday with outbreaks of
OL,12,Frain, drier later. Dry and bright on
OL,13,FFriday and Saturday. Strengthening
OL,14,Fsouthwesterly winds across Shetland on
OL,15,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
